Package lawnlayer

Class Tile

  • java.lang.Object
    • lawnlayer.GameObject
      • lawnlayer.Tile
  • public class Tile
extends GameObject
    A subclass of GameObject for all tile objects in the game. This includes concrete tiles, grass tiles, border tiles, and path tiles.

      • isFloatingAround

        public boolean isFloatingAround​(TileList otherTiles)
        Checks if this Tile is floating around the specified otherTiles.

        Retrieves the adjacent tiles of this Tile. Then, returns true if none of the adjacent tiles are contained in the otherTiles. Returns false otherwise.

        Parameters:
        otherTiles - the TileList in which this Tile is to be checked against for floating
        Returns:
        true if this Tile is floating

        true if this Tile is out of bounds

      • turnRed

        public void turnRed​(processing.core.PImage redPathSprite,
                    int frameCount)
        Turns this (green path) Tile into a red one.

        Sets the sprite of the Tile to the specified red path sprite, sets the frame of collision to the specified frameCount, and updates isRed to true.

        Parameters:
        redPathSprite - the PImage sprite this Tile is to be set to
        frameCount - the frame this Tile's frame of collision is to be set to
